object.name: TutorialText
object.text: Keep an eye out for hidden areas. Try accessing this one by crouching and moving into the wall by the platform.

object.name: TutorialText
object.text: Use enemies to reach far away platforms or hard to reach areas.

object.name: TutorialText
object.text: Some enemies, when jumped on will not die but instead give the player a higher jump! Try getting to the exit by jumping on this frog.
